Fonts (you must own licenses from the designers):

1) Puffberry — StuArt Foundry
   Save as: Puffberry.woff2 (and optionally Puffberry.woff)
   https://www.fontspring.com/fonts/stuart-foundry/puffberry (or your vendor)

2) Perfect Lemonade — Keithzo
   Save as: PerfectLemonade.woff2 (and optionally PerfectLemonade.woff)
   Check the designer's shop / MyFonts / etc. for the exact purchase link.

Place the files in this folder. The CSS in css/style.css already points to:
  ../fonts/Puffberry.woff2
  ../fonts/PerfectLemonade.woff2

If your files use different names, rename them to match OR edit the @font-face urls in css/style.css.

Until the files are added, the site uses similar free fallbacks (Fredoka One, Comic Neue) from Google Fonts in the HTML.
